+## Overview
+
+Total revenue was $7,154.44 across 30 orders. The median order value was $204.95.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget led product revenue at $2,392.00, followed by Widget at $2,118.94, Doohickey at $1,513.00, and Sprocket at $1,130.50.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North generated the most revenue at $2,176.35. East produced $1,830.79, South $1,732.48, and West $1,414.82.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget availability because it generated the highest product revenue at $2,392.00.
+- Study North's sales mix and apply relevant tactics to West, which trailed North by $761.53.
+- Promote Widget alongside Gadget; together they contributed $4,510.94, or 63.05% of total revenue.
